{"tid":2218843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐佈慎入！男子腹痛感菊花「萬頭鑽洞」　竟是5公尺絛蟲塞住屎眼","createTime":"2020-09-26T13:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T13:59:05.000Z","uid":333488,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"32cc909e1f91edcc83c4c0817e4a777d7782d7b0","tid":2218843,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ho91DHh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHo91DHh.jpg&h=9fac77f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國一名34歲男子杜安昌(Duangchan Dachyoddee)，在本月21日晚間突然感到腹部劇烈疼痛，他趕緊跑去上廁所，但他深深感覺到下體有如「萬頭鑽洞」，後來他自己發現，竟然是一條絛蟲卡死肛門，最後他嚇得趕緊就醫<br />\n據泰國《Thai Ch8》與《Liveleak》資訊報導，杜安昌在周一傍晚突然感覺到腹部疼痛，他趕緊跑去上廁所。但杜安昌上到一半，突然感覺有東西在他的下體萬頭攢動，隨後他更發現，自己的肛門竟然生出絛蟲，清晰可見絛蟲的頭部已經浸在馬桶水中，但絛蟲還有一半的身軀，卡在他的肛門之中。之後杜安昌費盡吃奶之力氣，用力把絛蟲從體內拉出，並用手輔助挖出，最後絛蟲終於全部排出體內，但這條絛蟲的長度，竟然長達5公尺。<br />\n杜安昌被眼前的絛蟲嚇到，他也立刻帶著絛蟲就醫，醫師研判，杜安昌應該是太常吃生肉，而寄生在生肉裡的蟲蟲，進入杜安昌的腸胃內產卵，最後更養出5公尺的無鉤絛蟲(taenia saginata)，又俗稱叫牛肉絛蟲。杜安昌也承認，他平時最喜歡吃的食物就是「Key Neua」，這是一種泰國傳統小吃，辣醬拌著生牛肉。<br />\n醫生指出，杜安昌的腸胃內應該還有蟲卵，因此他開了一些具有殺蟲功能的藥物，讓杜安昌服用。醫生也說，這幾天杜安昌還會排出含有無鉤絛蟲的排泄物，這讓杜安昌覺得有點噁心，但他也坦言，目前身體狀況已經比之前好多了。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"19bd6a2a38dd01e843224e3151f15dcf43eb2e29","tid":2218843,"uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:20:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200926/3PLMEZTQIFEYRHDTJCTQ6MASSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200926%2F3PLMEZTQIFEYRHDTJCTQ6MASSE%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=602c5aa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200926%2F3PLMEZTQIFEYRHDTJCTQ6MASSE%2F&h=ceebee0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200926/3PLMEZTQIFEYRHDTJCTQ6MASSE/</a>"},{"pid":"cda617428fd0cbf267658e3b41e0a7e43bdb728b","tid":2218843,"uid":195944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"施旖婕專報依啲 一係報咸濕新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a43097ec2e35f3accdb74b024bb7a4645b84be","tid":2218843,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:33:37.000Z","msg":"之後該男子對這感覺不能忘懷<br />\n從此...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f1c0827f0297e781a8aa36178e27e1293e5d4c","tid":2218843,"uid":234553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:35:14.000Z","msg":"仆你個街呢啲就高清大圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b047f4b0b8f3f39a32a47b8029ef5da1616b86","tid":2218843,"uid":116143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"麵條黎姐,呃我唔到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/shaking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf49f8a363c974f102145687f11ef15b23f4430","tid":2218843,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:59:05.000Z","msg":"仆街<br />\n細個食過啲生牛肉河粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}